.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTPAYS-AMOUNT-RANGE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listpays-amount-range \- FEAT-2041 verb
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listpays-amount-range
.RI [ min_msat
.IR max_msat ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
node-listpays-amount-range for lightning CLI (FEAT-2041).
.PP
Without arguments, returns a summary of all completed payments including
the overall min and max amount_sent_msat. With two arguments (min_msat and
max_msat), filters completed payments to those within the given range.
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
